{"about_the_game":"Form your platoon and take control in this WW2 tabletop turn-base strategy game. Defeat the enemy using tactics and luck and clear the stages with various puzzles and objectives. <br><br>In this game you will control a WW2 infantry platoon with its man in charge captain Williams. Some challenges will have a set pieces of units while others will have you composite your own platoon and figure out the best way to clear a stage. The game requires you to clear a stage and keep the captain alive while also adding a luck factor on top of a tabletop game by introducing dice roll tables.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080020/extras/Game3.png?t=1734994850\" /><br><br>Gameplay: You control 5 types of units - Captain, Private, Sniper, Medic and Mortar support. Each unit has a specific set of abilities that you need to utilize in order to clear a map. All units have 2 ability points per turn and various move distance, ranges and special abilities.<br>The traditional attrition system is replaced with dice rolls and various statuses that disables units prompting various tactic when managing the battlefield mixed with luck factor of a dice. <br>Game is played on a grid like map where you manage your troops around obstacles and covers where you use said terrain to gain advantage on a roll table, cover your troops with smoke and call air strikes. <br>Every game is a new experience when you balance strategy with luck!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080020/extras/Game4.png?t=1734994850\" /><br><br>Game features various levels with increasing difficulty and challenge modes both with in game star collection witch makes this game perfect casual single player couch time sink.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"SHARPSHOOTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3080020/7fa59a48b549ee9f